OL,3,CUK supermarkets warn business rates
OL,4,Crise could push up food inflation
OL,6,FBosses of the UK's biggest
OL,7,Fsupermarkets are urging the Chancellor
OL,8,Fto exempt shops from a new business
OL,9,Frates surtax, warning that shoppers
OL,10,Fwill bear the brunt of higher costs.
OL,12,FA letter, organised by industry group
OL,13,Fthe British Retail Consortium (BRC)
OL,14,Fand addressed to Rachel Reeves, argues
OL,15,Fthat limiting the tax burden on
OL,16,Fgrocers would help tackle food
OL,17,Finflation.
