OL,3,CUK supermarkets warn business rates
OL,4,Crise could push up food inflation
OL,6,FIt has been signed by UK executives
OL,7,Fand directors at Tesco, Sainsbury's,
OL,8,FAldi, Asda, Iceland, Lidl, Marks &
OL,9,FSpencer, Morrisons and Waitrose.
OL,11,FThe BRC said it is concerned that
OL,12,Flarge shops could see their business
OL,13,Frates rise if they are included in the
OL,14,FGovernment's new surtax for properties
OL,15,Fwith a rateable value over #500,000.
OL,17,FThis is expected to cover discounts
OL,18,Ffor smaller high-street firms, which
OL,19,Fwill be subject to reduced business
OL,20,Frates under the Government's plans.
