OL,3,CUK supermarkets warn business rates
OL,4,Crise could push up food inflation
OL,6,FThe letter concludes by asking Ms
OL,7,FReeves to "address retail's
OL,8,Fdisproportionate tax burden" which it
OL,9,Fsaid would "send a strong signal of
OL,10,Fsupport for the industry and of the
OL,11,FGovernment's commitment to tackling
OL,12,Ffood inflation".
OL,14,FHelen Dickinson, the BRC's chief
OL,15,Fexecutive, said: "Supermarkets are
OL,16,Fdoing everything possible to keep food
OL,17,Fprices affordable, but it's an uphill
OL,18,Fbattle, with over #7 billion in
OL,19,Fadditional costs in 2025 alone.
